---
title: Grilled Lemon Scented Coley with Veggie Packed Golden Pilaf
description: Coley is a mild tasting white fish with a a similar meaty texture to cod making it a really versatile ingredient to cook with. Seasoned with fresh lemon zest, a drizzle of olive oil, and baked until opaque in the centre, it’s flaky texture works really well with the vegetable-packed turmeric rice. Serve with a cooling dollop of yoghurt and finish off with some fresh chilli for those who like the heat. This is a real dinner winner the whole family will love.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grilled-lemon-scented-coley-4b510a63-016581a8.jpg
